gate: OPEN
task: S74-TD2
title: Fix Settings Menu Functionality
description: |
  The settings menu from S71-T09 is not properly functional. Fix all issues:
  - Verify SettingsScreen.tsx is properly integrated
  - Check that settings API endpoints are working (GET/POST /ws/settings)
  - Ensure settings persistence works across app restarts
  - Test all settings controls (language, theme, notifications, etc.)
  - Verify proper navigation to/from settings
  - Fix any broken settings UI components or forms

acceptance:
  - Settings menu opens correctly from all entry points
  - All settings options are functional and persist
  - Settings changes take effect immediately
  - No console errors when accessing settings
  - Settings are properly synchronized with server

requires: []
estimated: 4 hours
